cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.HC, cs.CR, cs.SY 

The paper discusses the use of human body communication (HBC) for social networking and secure authentication, which falls under the categories of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper proposes a new technique for interference-robust HBC, which could also fall under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
